Bus from Kitzbuhel to Bicklalm chairlft. Climb to Stuckkogel. Walk to Lammerbichlalm for lunch, walk to Kitzbuehler Horn TI-461, then travel back via cable car from Horn or Alpenhaus gondola. Walk back to the hotel in Kitzbuhel. Ryedale Walking Group led walk by OE/G4OBK/P in August 2019.
track_title: Bichlalm chairlift top to Stuckkogel then Kitzbueler Horn
